    %% Evaluation & Monitoring
    H --> R[RAGAS Evaluation]
    I --> S[Performance Monitoring - LangSmith]
    H --> T[Quality Assessment]
    I --> U[Business Impact]
    
    %% Response Flow
    O --> V[Generate Response]
    V --> W[Return to Frontend]
    W --> X[Display Results]
    
